glibmm: glibmm (C++ Bindings for GLib)
glibmm: 
glibmm: glibmm is the official C++ interface for the popular GUI library
glibmm: GLib. Highlights include typesafe callbacks, and a comprehensive set
glibmm: of widgets that are easily extensible via inheritance. You can 
glibmm: create user interfaces either in code or with the Glade User 
glibmm: Interface designer, using libglademm. There's extensive documentation,
glibmm: including API reference and a tutorial.  glibmm is free software
glibmm: distributed under LGPL. 
glibmm: 
